headline: From Icon to Movie Star - MR. PEANUT® Joins the Cast of The Electric State, On Netflix Friday, March 14
summary: In a captivating new chapter, MR. PEANUT® and the world-famous PLANTERS® NUTmobile are making their movie debut in Netflix's highly anticipated new film, The Electric State.
